HID: sony: Use the SIXAXIS_CONTROLLER constant when possible

Instead of checking for SIXAXIS_CONTROLLER_USB and SIXAXIS_CONTROLLER_BT
separately, a check on SIXAXIS_CONTROLLER can be used when setting
connect_mask.

